aws s3 mb s3://your-terraform-state-bucket --region ap-northeast-2
aws dynamodb create-table \
    --table-name your-terraform-state-lock-table \
    --attribute-definitions AttributeName=LockID,AttributeType=S \
    --key-schema AttributeName=LockID,KeyType=HASH \
    --provisioned-throughput ReadCapacityUnits=5,WriteCapacityUnits=5 \
    --region ap-northeast-2


aws eks update-kubeconfig --name my-app-eks-cluster --region ap-northeast-2


처음 구성 할 때

kubectl get pod 가 안됨

그 이유는 cluster 엔드포인트에서 private에서 외부 통신 다막아서 안됨

그래서

#############
  cluster_endpoint_public_access  = true
  #endpoint_private_access = true
  cluster_endpoint_public_access_cidrs  = ["1.233.102.123/32"]

################

  적용 해야됨